XYDiagram.name: Barren Komatiite MgO vs Ni (Barnes et al, 2004)
XYDiagram.Comment: MgO vs Ni plot for barren komatiite units
Classification fields are based on data density percentile contours enclosing 90th and 50th percentiles on data points from barren Komatiite samples.
XYDiagram.Reference: Barnes, SJ, Hill, RET, Perring, CS & Dowling, SE, 2004. Lithogeochemical exploration for komatiite-associated Ni-sulfide deposits: strategies and limitations. Mineralogy and Petrology, 82, 259-293.
